The,Tracking,Notification,API,allows,developers,to,provide,customers,with,tracking,alerts,for,packages,they,are,sending,with,New,Zealand,Post,Designed,for,use,alongside,the,Tracking,API,this,service,provides,updates,via,email,SMS,or,webhook,and,allows,developers,to,specify,which,events,initiate,messages,create,user,friendly,aliases,for,tracking,numbers,and,customize,notifications